      • deviceNotificationsFetched

        public void deviceNotificationsFetched(AylaDevice device,
                                       AylaDeviceNotification[] notifications,
                                       AylaError error)
        Called when the helper class has fetched the array of AylaDeviceNotifications for the given device.
        参数:
        device - Device notifications were fetched for. The notifications will be contained in the Device.getDevice().deviceNotifications array.
        notifications - Returned array of notifications for the device
        error - Error object if one occurred, otherwise null

      • appNotificationsFetched

        public void appNotificationsFetched(AylaDevice device,
                                    AylaDeviceNotification deviceNotification,
                                    AylaDeviceNotificationApp[] notificationApps,
                                    AylaError error)
        Called when the helper class has fetched an array of AylaAppNotifications for a particular AylaDeviceNotification. Generally used internally to this class. However, implementers may choose to override this method to gain more visibility into the steps taken to deal with notifications.
        参数:
        device - Device that owns these notifications
        deviceNotification - The AylaDeviceNotification that contains the newly fetched AylaAppNotification array.
        notificationApps - Notification apps attached to the deviceNotification
        error - Error object if an error occurred, otherwise null

      • deviceStateComplete

        public void deviceStateComplete(AylaDevice device,
                                AylaError error)
        Called when the helper class has fetched all of the AylaAppNotifications for each AylaDeviceNotification. The returned device will contain the device notifications, each of which will contain an array of app notifications under Device.getDevice.deviceNotifications[].appNotifications[].

        As the name of the method indicates, when this is called, the device will contain the complete array of device notifications and their own arrays of app notifications.

        参数:
        device - Device that has been updated to inclue all notifications and apps
        error - Error object if an error occurred, otherwise null

      • deviceNotificationUpdated

        public void deviceNotificationUpdated(AylaDevice device,
                                      AylaDeviceNotification notification,
                                      AylaServiceApp.NotificationType notificationType,
                                      AylaError error)
        Called when the helper class has added or removed a notification and its apps from the Device object. The returned device will contain the updated set of notifications and their apps.
        参数:
        device - Device that was modified
        notification - Notification object that was updated (added or removed)
        notificationType - email | sms | push
        error - Error object if an error occurred, otherwise null

      • newDeviceUpdated

        public void newDeviceUpdated(AylaDevice device,
                             AylaError error)
        Called in response to a call to initializeNewDeviceNotifications
        参数:
        device - Device that was updated
        error - Error object if an error occurred, otherwise null
